===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

#{{transitive}} To make (to appear) much smaller; to [[render]] [[puny]] or [[tiny]]
#:''The newly-built skyscraper '''dwarfs''' the older buildings that make up the rest of downtown.''
#:''Bach '''dwarfs''' all other composers.''

